node.text:
“To her, the name of father was another name for love.” —Fanny Fern ⁣
⁣
As we approach Father’s Day in the Me Too era, I reflect on some of the great role models in my life. I notice this list includes:⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Father⁣⁣s⁣
Grandfather⁣⁣s⁣
Godfathers⁣⁣⁣
Stepfather⁣⁣s⁣
Fur Fathers⁣⁣⁣
Father Figures⁣
⁣⁣⁣
These photos show the faces of the different fathers in my life. They were invited to Juan’s and my wedding for a reason. I just want to thank them for teaching the world how females should be treated.⁣
⁣
